description:
This plugin allows you to quickly insert the time into the editor using the "/" command. The following configurations are for different time templates.
Name: The name of the template.
Filter: The command name that follows "/", multiple commands are separated by a ",".
Template: The formatted template for the time, for example, yyyy-MM-dd E (EEEE-e; 周ECN) HH:mm:ss represents 2024-08-19 Mon (Monday-1; 周一) 00:05:58
confirmreset: All templates will be reset to default
